@model Compass.ViewModels.Modern.AdminFipsSimplePanelModel
<div class="admin-panel">
 <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">@Model.Heading</h2>
  @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.IntroHtml))
  {
 <div class="govuk-body dfe-c-text-muted dfe-c-mb-2">@Html.Raw(Model.IntroHtml)</div>
  }

  @if (Model.Rows.Count == 0)
  {
 <p class="govuk-body">No @(Model.EntityLabel)s configured.</p>
  }
  else
  {
 <div class="dfe-f-table-wrapper" data-module="dfe-f-table">
  <div class="govuk-visually-hidden" aria-live="polite" data-dfe-table-sort-live></div>
      <table class="govuk-table govuk-table--small dfe-f-table--condensed">
        <thead class="govuk-table__head">
          <tr class="govuk-table__row">
 <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header" aria-sort="none"><button type="button" class="dfe-f-table-sort-button">Name</button></th>
 <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header" aria-sort="none"><button type="button" class="dfe-f-table-sort-button">Description</button></th>
 <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header" aria-sort="none"><button type="button" class="dfe-f-table-sort-button">Order</button></th>
 <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header" aria-sort="none"><button type="button" class="dfe-f-table-sort-button">Status</button></th>
 <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header govuk-table__header--numeric"><span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Actions</span></th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
          @foreach (var row in Model.Rows)
          {
            <tr class="govuk-table__row">
              <td class="govuk-table__cell"><strong>@row.Name</strong></td>
              <td class="govuk-table__cell">@(string.IsNullOrEmpty(row.Description) ? "—" : row.Description)</td>
              <td class="govuk-table__cell">@row.SortOrder</td>
              <td class="govuk-table__cell">
                @if (row.IsActive)
 { <span class="dfe-f-badge dfe-f-badge--small dfe-f-badge--green">Active</span> }
                else
 { <span class="dfe-f-badge dfe-f-badge--small dfe-f-badge--grey">Inactive</span> }
              </td>
              <td class="govuk-table__cell" style="text-align:right;">
                <form method="post" action="@Url.Action(Model.ToggleActionName, "ModernAdmin", new { id = row.Id })" style="display:inline;">
                  @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
 <button type="submit" class="govuk-button govuk-button--secondary govuk-button--small govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">@(row.IsActive ? "Deactivate" : "Activate")</button>
                </form>
              </td>
            </tr>
          }
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  }

 <details class="govuk-details" style="margin-top:1rem;">
 <summary class="govuk-details__summary"><span class="govuk-details__summary-text">Add @Model.EntityLabel</span></summary>
 <form method="post" action="@Model.AddActionUrl" class="govuk-form-group">
      @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
 <div class="govuk-form-group">
 <label class="govuk-label" for="fsl-name">Name</label>
 <input class="govuk-input govuk-input--width-20" id="fsl-name" name="name" required>
      </div>
 <div class="govuk-form-group">
 <label class="govuk-label" for="fsl-desc">Description</label>
 <input class="govuk-input govuk-input--width-30" id="fsl-desc" name="description">
      </div>
 <div class="govuk-form-group">
 <label class="govuk-label" for="fsl-order">Display order</label>
 <input class="govuk-input govuk-input--width-5" id="fsl-order" name="displayOrder" type="number" value="0">
      </div>
 <button type="submit" class="govuk-button">Add</button>
    </form>
  </details>
</div>
